	<header class="page-header">
				<h2 class="title-secondary">Careers</h2>
				<h1 class="title-primary">
							Benefits					</h1>
								
				<h3 class="header-text">An extraordinary career comes with exceptional benefits.</h3>
						</header>
			<article class="col-main content">
			<p>Citadel challenges its team members every day. In turn, we recognize and reward their results. We offer a highly competitive, comprehensive range of benefits that simplify and enhance their everyday lives.</p>
		</article>
	</section><section class="row module-text col1-layout full-width bkg-lgt-blue lines">
	<article class="col-main">
		<div class="content">
							<h2 class="section-title">Benefits Overview</h2>
						<p class="text-style-3">We offer the following benefits to our employees worldwide:</p>
<div class="col3-set benefits-bullets">
<div class="col-1">
<ul class="border-lines">
<li>Medical and dental plans</li>
<li>Retirement savings plan</li>
<li>Vacation and sick time</li>
<li>Short- and long-term disability coverage</li>
<li>Wellness initiatives</li>
</ul>
</div>
<div class="col-2">
<ul class="border-lines">
<li>Travel insurance</li>
<li>Educational reimbursement</li>
<li>Transit benefits</li>
<li>On-site professional development</li>
<li>Teladoc coverage</li>
</ul>
</div>
<div class="col-3">
<ul class="border-lines">
<li>Access to fitness facilities</li>
<li>Backup child care</li>
<li>Employee Assistance Program</li>
<li>Life Insurance</li>
<li>Flexible spending accounts</li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>
					</div>
	</article>
